name: Willow (itch) (normalmilkguy)
description:
In Willows you play as a leaf boy named Liko. your objective is to grow a tree in the centre of the village, the tree is the source of the villages power, but the tree is slowely dying. go on a quest to save the tree and bring peace to th village :D

WASD to move

Space to jump

E to interact
